---
// Claude Code integration callout section
// Highlights the floimg-claude plugin for AI-assisted image workflows
---

<section class="claude-callout">
  <div class="callout-container">
    <div class="callout-badge">
      <svg class="claude-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <path
          d="M12 2L2 7L12 12L22 7L12 2Z"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
        <path
          d="M2 17L12 22L22 17"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
        <path
          d="M2 12L12 17L22 12"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
      </svg>
      <span>Claude Code Integration</span>
    </div>

    <h2 class="callout-title">Built for AI Agents</h2>

    <p class="callout-description">
      The <code>floimg-claude</code> plugin gives Claude Code native image workflow capabilities. Generate
      charts, process images, and build complex pipelines through natural conversation.
    </p>

    <div class="callout-features">
      <div class="feature">
        <span class="feature-icon">ðŸ¤–</span>
        <div>
          <strong>MCP Server</strong>
          <p>Model Context Protocol for seamless AI integration</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <span class="feature-icon">âš¡</span>
        <div>
          <strong>Natural Language</strong>
          <p>"Create a chart showing Q4 revenue" just works</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <span class="feature-icon">ðŸ”§</span>
        <div>
          <strong>Full Pipeline Access</strong>
          <p>All generators and transforms available to Claude</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="callout-code">
      <div class="code-header">
        <span class="code-label">claude_desktop_config.json</span>
      </div>
      <pre><code>{`{
  "mcpServers": {
    "floimg": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["-y", "@teamflojo/floimg-claude"]
    }
  }
}`}</code></pre>
    </div>

    <a href="/docs/integrations/claude-code" class="callout-cta">
      Learn more about Claude Code integration â†’
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .claude-callout {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(13 148 136 / 0.1), rgb(20 184 166 / 0.05));
    border-top: 1px solid rgb(13 148 136 / 0.2);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(13 148 136 / 0.2);
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
  }

  :global(.dark) .claude-callout {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(13 148 136 / 0.15), rgb(20 184 166 / 0.05));
  }

  .callout-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .callout-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    background: rgb(13 148 136);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .claude-icon {
    width: 1.25rem;
    height: 1.25rem;
  }

  .callout-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--sl-color-text);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .callout-description {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: #52525b;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  :global(.dark) .callout-description {
    color: #a1a1aa;
  }

  .callout-description code {
    background: rgb(13 148 136 / 0.15);
    color: rgb(13 148 136);
    padding: 0.125rem 0.375rem;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    font-size: 0.95em;
  }

  :global(.dark) .callout-description code {
    background: rgb(13 148 136 / 0.25);
    color: rgb(45 212 191);
  }

  .callout-features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .callout-features {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .feature {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    text-align: left;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: var(--sl-color-bg);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid #e4e4e7;
  }

  :global(.dark) .feature {
    border-color: #27272a;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .feature strong {
    display: block;
    color: var(--sl-color-text);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .feature p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #52525b;
    margin: 0;
  }

  :global(.dark) .feature p {
    color: #a1a1aa;
  }

  .callout-code {
    background: var(--m-code-bg, #1e1e2e);
    border: 1px solid var(--m-code-border, #3f3f46);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-align: left;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }

  .code-header {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--m-code-border, #3f3f46);
  }

  .code-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #a1a1aa;
    font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace;
  }

  .callout-code pre {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 1rem;
    overflow-x: auto;
    background: transparent;
  }

  .callout-code code {
    color: var(--m-code-text, #e4e4e7);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace;
  }

  .callout-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    color: rgb(13 148 136);
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .callout-cta:hover {
    color: rgb(20 184 166);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  :global(.dark) .callout-cta {
    color: rgb(45 212 191);
  }
</style>
